'''Romodi Interstellar''' was a major starline that existed shortly before the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. It was based on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. It was sued for negligence in the case of the hijacked ''[[Elegant Wake]]'' in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]].

